    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《乔伊的箱子》中，玩家将化身为一名孩子，探索弥漫着罪恶与阴影的公寓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追随记忆与线索，穿越梦境与现实的边界只为找回失踪的挚友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/0cab59847656b5cc6568e9749ea5c576.poster.avif?t=1765469350\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/0cab59847656b5cc6568e9749ea5c576.webm?t=1765469350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/0cab59847656b5cc6568e9749ea5c576.mp4?t=1765469350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >穿梭在梦境与现实之间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >徜徉于孩子幻想出的奇异世界，<br>却在下一秒坠入污秽破败的公寓。<br>在梦与现实的裂缝中解开谜题、辨别真假，<br>寻找逃离这场噩梦的唯一出口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/c4a681ab752bfc471f95ce70e08f3b07.poster.avif?t=1765469350\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/c4a681ab752bfc471f95ce70e08f3b07.webm?t=1765469350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/c4a681ab752bfc471f95ce70e08f3b07.mp4?t=1765469350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >公寓的住户都有秘密</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里居住着形形色色的奇怪住户<br>神秘养胎的房东夫妇、<br>被众人避开的屠夫、<br>沉迷禁忌实验的密医……<br>他们的行为都被某种无形的力量所操控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/239c0b3adf29c95c1fb9cbc651d30043.poster.avif?t=1765469350\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/239c0b3adf29c95c1fb9cbc651d30043.webm?t=1765469350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223260/extras/239c0b3adf29c95c1fb9cbc651d30043.mp4?t=1765469350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >孩子们的勇气，对抗无形的恶意</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑暗之中，唯有天真仍闪烁微光。<br>为了找回失踪的朋友，孩子们踏上与罪恶抗争的旅程。<br>那些消失的孩子究竟去了哪里？<br>唯有勇气，能揭开真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
